## 6. Files in `.ralph/`

| File | Purpose | Tracked by git? |
|---|---|---|
| `prompt.md`     | Agent instructions (the contract). **Don't edit lightly** | yes |
| `ralph.<ext>`   | Loop driver | yes |
| `RUNBOOK.md`    | This file | yes |
| `progress.txt`  | Per-iteration progress + codebase patterns | **no** (gitignored ŌĆö too noisy) |
| `.lock`         | Runtime lock; created at startup, removed at exit | no (gitignored) |
| `.complete`     | Sentinel set by agent when all stories `passed` | no (gitignored) |
| `.commit-failure` | (v1.1) JSON sentinel set by driver after a `git commit` failed; tracks retry counter; agent reads it at iteration start to enter repair flow, deletes it after successful repair | no (gitignored) |
| `.stop`         | (v1.2) external graceful-stop signal ŌĆö `touch` it from another terminal, driver picks it up at next iteration boundary and exits 0 cleanly | no (gitignored) |
| `package.json`  | (js runtime only) `{"type":"commonjs"}` to isolate driver from parent ESM | yes |

